---
title: Mediterranean Fish Stew with Couscous and Parsley Dressing
description: Fresh, zesty and wholesome, our Mediterranean-inspired fish stew is the perfect one-pot recipe for any night of the week. In this dish, our delicious seafood mix is gently combined in a rich vegetable packed stew and steamed until cooked through. We’ve served this delicious stew with a simple couscous salad and finished everything off with a delicious parsley dressing for a real taste of the Mediterranean.
